Shift and Hours
8-hour shift
&nbsp;
Location
Beja
&nbsp;
Full Job Description
Job Description
Intelcia, currently operating in 17 countries and 48 sites, provides global services and a multi-service experience, both onshore and offshore, to meet the challenges of globalization, covering the entire customer relationship management value chain.
We are currently recruiting for a position in Beja!
Position: Customer Support (Portuguese Speaking)
Description
- Receiving customer service calls (by phone);
- Providing billing information, clarifications, managing complaints, registering orders/changes to the telecommunications tariff, and promoting with a focus on customer quality and satisfaction.
Benefits:
- Paid training;
- Employment contract;
- Base salary + meal allowance + vacation and Christmas bonuses;
- Monthly Performance bonus + Commissions;
- Health insurance;
- Positive, technology-driven work environment with opportunities for growth/advancement.
Requirements:
- High school diploma;
- Basic computer skills (from the p.o.v of the user);
- Excellent communication and empathy skills;
- Proactive, dynamic, and assertive.
Hours: Full-Time 40 hours and Part-Time 25 hours between 12 PM and 12 AM, Monday to Sunday, with two days off per week.
